âœ… 4. Product Recommendation System

Built using collaborative filtering & cosine similarity

Suggests relevant products based on similarity and purchase patterns

Example Code:

from sklearn.metrics.pairwise import cosine_similarity

similarity_matrix = cosine_similarity(pivot_table)
recommended_items = np.argsort(similarity_matrix[item_id])[::-1][1:6]


Business Impact:

Increases basket value

Improves personalization

Enhances customer lifetime value

